Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:33.68,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lend my ear{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.38,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Voices inside{\i}
